      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based dry pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> pumpkin seeds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p><p>Once golden, transfer the <strong>toasted pumpkin seeds</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
