      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for an initial 8-10 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-8-1724080709088-x200.jpg",
