    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onions are softened, add the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>and 1/2 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 tsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[1 1/2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 4-5 min or until sticky and caramelised – these are your <strong>caramelised onions</strong></p>",
