    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>dressed leaves </strong>at the bottom of the plate and layer over the <strong>roasted pepper &</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>caramelised onions</strong> and <strong>garlic portobello mushroom</strong></p><p>Crumble over your <strong>goats' cheese</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> toasted pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
